Choose Weapon - utility skill
------------------------------------------------------------
When a swashbuckler nears the end of his training, he often
chooses a pair of blades that have served him particularly
well through his training. He will become so attuned to
those blades that they almost seem like extensions of
himself. Thereafter, whenever he uses his chosen blades,
he will fight with more skill when using swashbuckler
techniques. The choice may be made only once per boot and
of course both weapons must be blades. The swashbuckler is
so attuned to the chosen blades that even other blades of
the same kind will not be as good in his hands as the
two specifically chosen by him.

GL: 12
SP:  0
command:  choose [main|secondary] <weapon>
duration: remainder of uptime
